# Components

The following composite monitoring and alerting components are deployed as part of monitoring-environment (and some are accessible via browser):

| Component                     | Description                                                                            | Nonprod URL                | Prod URL                   |
| -----------------------       | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------|----------------------------|
| grafana                       | Grafana UI for viewing Standardised Platform, Product, Journey and Detailed Dashboards | <https://grafana>          | <https://grafana>          |
| prometheus                    | Prometheus UI to view raw metrics, alerts, rules, status and configuration             | <https://prometheus>       | <https://prometheus>       |
| alertmanager                  | Alertmanager UI to configure, silence and inhibit Alerts                               | <https://alertmanager>     | <https://alertmanager>     |
| thanos-query                  | Thanos Query                                                                           | <https://thanos-query>     | <https://thanos-query>     |
| thanos-ruler                  | Thanos Ruler                                                                           | <https://thanos-ruler>     | <https://thanos-ruler>     |
| thanos-sidecar                | Thanos Sidecar for Prometheus Server                                                   | not accessible via browser | not accessible via browser |
| thanos-store-gateway          | Thanos Store Gateway                                                                   | not accessible via browser | not accessible via browser |
| thanos-compactor              | Thanos Compactor                                                                       | not accessible via browser | not accessible via browser |
| yace                          | Yet Another Cloudwatch Exporter                                                        | not accessible via browser | not accessible via browser |
| gitlab-exporter               | Gitlab Exporter (HCS Gitlab)                                                           | not accessible via browser | not accessible via browser |
